message: To achieve a score of 100, you need to combine three items: one grain, one vegetable, and one protein. Crucially, all three items must be cooked exactly once. For grains (like bread or rice), you *must* soak them with water first, then cook the soaked grain with the stove. For vegetables and proteins, cook them once with the stove. Do not cook any item more than once, or it will lose value. Once you have a cooked grain, cooked vegetable, and cooked protein, combine them to get 100 points.
